## lib/ Top-Level Structure

```
lib/
├── core/         ← shared infrastructure (always present)
│   ├── foundation/  ← Pure Dart only
│   ├── platform/    ← Flutter/OS wrappers
│   ├── infra/       ← Implementation + network + errors
│   └── di/          ← Composition root
├── modules/      ← optional bounded runtime modules (e.g. sync)
├── Features/     ← feature slices (data/domain/presentation)
├── presentation/ ← shared UI: theme, error, feedback, locale, pagination
├── shared/       ← shared widgets across features
├── routes/       ← auto_route router
├── resources/    ← generated locale keys, assets helpers
└── new/          ← optional alternate stacks (graphql backup)
```

---

## Core Internal Layers

```
core/
├── foundation/   ← Pure Dart only. No Flutter, no Dio, no I/O.
├── platform/     ← Flutter/OS wrappers. Depends on foundation only.
├── infra/        ← Implementation. Depends on foundation + platform.
└── di/           ← Composition root (only place that imports everything)
```

### Dependency Rules (Strict)

```
foundation  → nothing from platform, infra, or Flutter     ✅
platform    → foundation only                               ✅
infra       → foundation + platform                         ✅
di          → everything (composition root exception)       ✅
modules     → foundation + infra only                       ✅
Features    → foundation + infra + modules (NOT other Features) ✅
presentation → foundation + infra + platform (AppLocale only via locale/) ✅

core        → Features      ❌ NEVER (except di/)
core        → presentation  ❌ NEVER (except di/)
core        → routes        ❌ NEVER (except di/)
modules     → Features      ❌ NEVER
modules     → presentation  ❌ NEVER
Features    → Features      ❌ NEVER
```

---

## Layer Contents

**foundation/** — `Failure` sealed types (10), `BaseUseCase`, `Params`, `ApiResponse<T>`, `PaginationQuery`, `AuthNetworkGateway`, `LocaleProvider`, `SessionReader`, `validators`, `num_extensions`

**platform/** — `LogService`, `PersistenceKeys`, `MediaService`, `UrlLauncher`, `AppBlocObserver`, `string_extensions`, `datetime_extensions`, `AppLocale` (enum), `AppSettings`, `ConnectivityService`, `NetworkStateMonitor`, `PermissionsService`, `AppFeatures` (central toggle), `LocalNotificationsService` + adapters, `BiometricsService`, `ClipboardService`, `ShareService`, `FileService`, `AppLifecycleService` + adapters, `StorageService`, `SecureStorageService`, `EncryptionService` + adapters

**infra/** — `env/flavors`, `network` (rest/interceptors/boundary/cancellation), `errors` (mappers/registry), `session` (AuthEventBus, LocaleProviderImpl)

**di/** — `injection.dart` (entry + calls PlatformServicesRegistry), `injection_module.dart` (always-on), `platform_services_registry.dart` (optional P6-P10), `injection.config.dart` (generated)

**modules/sync/** — optional offline sync engine. Entry: `SyncSDK.initialize(config, getIt)`

