## Presentation Layer (ليس core/)

```
presentation/
├── theme/        ← AppColors, AppPalette, AppTheme, ThemeExtensions
├── extensions/   ← BuildContext helpers (screen size, padding, dialog, bottomsheet)
├── error/        ← FailureUiMapper, UiAction
├── feedback/     ← AppFeedbackService (abstract), adapters, context.feedback.*
├── locale/       ← LocaleSwitcher variants, context.isAr / context.isRtl / context.changeLocale()
└── shared/       ← PaginationCubit, ConnectivityCubit
```

**قاعدة:** لا تضع feedback أو locale أو PaginationCubit أو theme داخل `core/`.

