## Errors Flow

```
Exception (Dio/IO/unknown)
    ▼ infra/errors/
FailureMapperRegistry.map(error) → Failure (sealed type)
    ▼ presentation/error/
FailureUiMapper.toAction(failure) → UiAction
    ▼ Feature/cubits/
switch على كل حالة → emit State
```

- `foundation/errors/` = أنواع Failure فقط — لا mapping، لا Dio، لا `.tr()`
- `infra/errors/` = mapping فقط — لا UI، لا localization
- `presentation/error/` = عرض فقط — لا منطق
- Repositories = `handle()` من BaseRepository — لا try/catch يدوي
- Cubits = `FailureUiMapper.toAction(failure)` — لا يعرف DioException

