## Cubit Error Pattern

```dart
res.fold((failure) {
  switch (FailureUiMapper.toAction(failure)) {
    case ShowError(:final message): emit(State.error(message));
    case NavigateToLogin(): AuthEventBus.instance.emit(AuthEvent.sessionExpired);
    case Silent(): break;
  }
}, (data) => emit(State.success(data)));
```

