## Do NOT Put in Core

- Theme, BuildContext extensions, PaginationCubit → `presentation/`
- AppFeedbackService adapters → `presentation/feedback/adapters/`
- LocaleSwitcher → `presentation/locale/`
- GraphQL → `new/09_graphql/` (لا تربطه بـ lib/)
- Feature ApiService, models → `Features/<name>/data/`
- Optional modules (sync) → `modules/`

